WEBVTT

00:00:29.746 --> 00:00:33.162
domestic violence is typically seen
as a private matter.

00:00:34.037 --> 00:00:38.996
Neighbors, however, are quick to react
to any other kind of noise.

00:00:40.412 --> 00:00:44.121
We wanted to expose and affect
the absurdity of this.

00:00:44.871 --> 00:00:47.412
So we designed an experiment.

00:00:48.204 --> 00:00:52.246
We rented the apartment
just below V's for one night.

00:00:52.996 --> 00:00:54.579
And at 10pm,

00:00:54.621 --> 00:00:57.412
Maksim, the artist in our group,

00:00:57.454 --> 00:01:00.954
sat on the drum set
we had assembled in the living room